<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.5.4">
<l>vampaviḻ kōtai poruṭṭā mālviṭai yēḻu maṭartta</l>
<l>cempava ḷattiraḷ vāyaṉ cirītaraṉ tolpukaḻ pāṭik</l>
<l>kumpiṭu naṭṭamiṭ ṭāṭik kōkukaṭ ṭuṇṭuḻa lātār</l>
<l>tampiṟap pālpaya ṉeṉṉē cātu caṉaṅka ḷiṭaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who do not roam, absorbing ???, dancing by putting a dance with folded hands,</l>
<l>singing the ancient fame of Śrīdhara, the one with a round red coral mouth</l>
<l>who killed seven big bulls for the sake of [the one with] the freshly opening garland,</l>
<l>what benefit by their birth among good folk?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
